title: TV ad pairs the mayor and Peskin — who’s behind the highjinks?
text:
Photo: Pete Kiehart, The Chronicle Clint Reilly, shown with Rep. Jackie Speier, paid for an ad linking Aaron Peskin and Mayor Ed Lee. Clint Reilly, shown with Rep. Jackie Speier, paid for an ad linking...
A new television ad urges San Franciscans to vote for former Supervisor Aaron Peskin for the District 3 seat and Mayor Ed Lee in the November election — a message that may be intended to harm the mayor instead of help him.
